message.content: cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.DS. The paper is concerned with the task of multi-hop open-domain Question Answering, which involves textual reasoning and efficient searching. This task is related to several sub-categories of computer science, including computational linguistics (cs.CL), information retrieval (cs.IR), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), machine learning (cs.LG), and data structures and algorithms (cs.DS). Therefore, these are the most likely sub-categories for this paper.
